  52. ‌let unsigned_to_int =
  53.   let max_int = of_int Stdlib.max_int in
  54.   fun n ->
  55.     if compare zero n <= 0 && compare n max_int <= 0 then
  56.       Some (to_int n)
  57.     else
  58.       None

  75. ‌let unsigned_compare n m =
  76.   compare (sub n min_int) (sub m min_int)

  78. ‌let min x y : t = if x <= y then x else y
  79. ‌let max x y : t = if x >= y then x else y

  81. (* Unsigned division from signed division of the same
  82.    bitness. See Warren Jr., Henry S. (2013). Hacker's Delight (2 ed.), Sec 9-3.
  83. *)
  84. ‌let unsigned_div n d =
  85.   if d < zero then
  86.     if unsigned_compare n d < 0 then zero else one
  87.   else
  88.     let q = shift_left (div (shift_right_logical n 1) d) 1 in
  89.     let r = sub n (mul q d) in
  90.     if unsigned_compare r d >= 0 then succ q else q

  92. ‌let unsigned_rem n d =
  93.   sub n (mul (unsigned_div n d) d)
